                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18480821-name-342" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18480821-name-342" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18480821-name-342" type="surname" value="WELLING"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18480821-name-342" type="given" value="PHOEBE"></interp>PHŒBE WELLING</persName>
                  </hi>. I am mistress of a school at London-wall—Mary Ann Bruce was my servant—I missed these articles (<hi rend="italic">produced</hi>), and many more, from a closet, which was locked—they are mine—Hannah Bruce used to come to wash.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18480821-name-343" type="witnessName">
