                        <interp inst="t18480821-name-343" type="surname" value="GREEN"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18480821-name-343" type="given" value="EDWARD"></interp>EDWARD GREEN</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a pawnbroker, at Chiswell-street—I produce a remnant of stuff, pawned on 11th July, by, I believe, both prisoners; also two pairs of stockings on 13th July, and some flannel and two towels on 3lst July, by one or other of the prisoners.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
