               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Hannah Bruce.</hi> I never pledged any of them.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Mary Ann Bruce.</hi> I was left in the house with Mary Swinton; she told me to pledge them, and said she would replace them; my mother is innocent.</p>
